The Correlator pod consumes observations made from our agent and transforms them into topology elements and telemetry.
When the latency of the transformation process is high we might have components and/or relations missing in the topology, and metrics
not present or arriving late.

### Investigate
There are a few potential causes of the high latency. To identify the root cause, please contact SUSE Observability [support](https://www.stackstate.com/company/contact-us/).